A chatbot is a piece of software that mimics human dialogue through text chats, voice commands, or both. 
Here are  some of the steps I followed to program a chatbot :
1. Decided  type of chatbot I needed. 
2. Determined my chatbot key performance indicator. 
3. Understood user needs.
4. Given my chatbot a personality. 
5. Planned  chatbot flow. 
6.Designed chatbot.
7. Previewed and tested your chatbot. 
8.Targeted chatbot.
9. Measured and optimised chatbot performance.
